WEBVTT

00:02:29.509 --> 00:02:31.806
and just, you know,
trying to tell one story.

00:02:31.830 --> 00:02:36.137
I particularly and personally
was accused of siding with,

00:02:36.161 --> 00:02:38.143
for instance, the citizens of Sarajevo --

00:02:38.167 --> 00:02:39.594
"siding with the Muslims,"

00:02:39.618 --> 00:02:42.670
because they were the minority
who were being attacked

00:02:42.694 --> 00:02:46.432
by Christians on the Serb side

00:02:46.456 --> 00:02:48.175
in this area.

00:02:48.199 --> 00:02:49.541
And it worried me.

00:02:49.565 --> 00:02:51.756
It worried me that I was being
accused of this.

00:02:51.780 --> 00:02:53.122
I thought maybe I was wrong,

00:02:53.146 --> 00:02:55.494
maybe I'd forgotten what objectivity was.

00:02:55.518 --> 00:02:58.525
But then I started to understand
that what people wanted

00:02:58.549 --> 00:03:00.347
was actually not to do anything --